----------------------------------
People Counting Demo Application
----------------------------------

* Deep learning application for people counting based on the detected heads.

----------------------------------
Steps to run the demo application	
----------------------------------

* Clone the repository,
	* git clone https://github.com/dilipkumar25/smartecam-ai-samples.git

* Change directory to repository directory,
	* cd smartecam-ai-samples

* Create directory structure,
	* mkdir -p /opt/econ/peoplecounting

* Copy the application into SmarteCam device,
	* sudo cp -r people_counting/* /opt/econ/peoplecounting

* Download the model file from google drive, 
	* https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ihiaK7jlyBdo9l8q5oucA-VUVOkoOU1D/view?usp=sharing

* Create directory,
	* sudo mkdir -p /opt/econ/peoplecounting/peoplecounting/econ/peopletracking/models/

* Copy the model file to the models location,
	* sudo cp <DOWNLOAD_PATH>/trt_head_detection_FP16.pb /opt/econ/peoplecounting/peoplecounting/econ/peopletracking/models/

* Download the video file from google drive,
	* https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vHtU3xPe5IERKz1_9Foq1xW88nS6yEsO/view?usp=sharing

* Copy the video file to videos location,
	* sudo cp <DOWNLOAD_PATH>/combined_videos.avi /opt/econ/peoplecounting/peoplecounting/econ/peopletracking/videos/

* Run the application using the command,
	* /opt/econ/peoplecounting/people_counting_demo

